      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "MatAnyone2 — Video Matting (VHS)\n\nBundled starter clip: matanyone2-demo-input.mp4\ninstall.py copies it into ComfyUI/input so this demo queues cleanly.\nSwap the Load Video node to your own footage any time.\n\n1. Queue once → Editor auto-opens on first frame\n2. Left-click = positive point · Right-click = negative point → Apply\n3. Queue again → Full matte renders\n\nModels (auto-downloaded on first use):\n• MatAnyone 2     github.com/pq-yang/MatAnyone2/releases  →  models/matanyone/\n• SAM ViT-H       dl.fbaipublicfiles.com/segment_anything/sam_vit_h_4b8939.pth  →  models/sams/\n\nRequires: ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite  ·  github.com/Kosinkadink/ComfyUI-VideoHelperSuite"
      ],
      "color": "#845b1c",
      "bgcolor": "#1d1309"
    },
